name: Rachael
description:
.  "You're reading a magasine. You come across a full page of nude photos of a girl." (Deckard)

"Just answer the questions please." (Deckard)
"You show it to your husband. He likes it so much he hangs it on your bedroom wall." (Deckard)

"I should be enough for him." (Rachael)
